<h2><strong>How to care for your handcrafted soap:&nbsp;</strong></h2>

<ul>
	<li>Don&#39;t let your soap sit in water.&nbsp;</li>
	<li>Store soap on a well drained soapdish.&nbsp;</li>
	<li>Allow soap plenty of fresh air todry between uses.&nbsp;</li>
	<li>Never place soap where shower water can hit it.&nbsp;</li>
	<li>If your your soap gets waterlogged and becomes gooey, simply put it on a draining soapdish for a few days and let it dry out thoroughly.&nbsp;</li>
</ul>

